description.value:
Papyrus written with black ink, demotic legal document dated to month of Phamenoth of year 17 of Ptolemy Euergetes I. 5 lines on recto, names of 16 witnesses on verso.
Thompson's MS Catalogue: "Divorce between the man of Syene Panofer called Pa-egosh (Pekusis) and his wife Tanofer daughter of Amenhotep. Scribe Amenhotep son of Hery (Erieus)".
Concerning Tanefer, cf. P BM EA 10073; on her divorce, cf. P BM EA 10079 B-C.
